uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.model

Interface AnonymisingComposite<BDO extends DataObject>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AvatarComposite, CertificateComposite, DatabasePasswordComposite, EmailNameFinder, GlobalNamePolicy, MultiKeyComposite, OldSingleKeyComposite, PublicKeyComposite, RealNameComposite, SingleKeyComposite, UUIDNamePolicy, WebNameFinder

    public interface AnonymisingComposite<BDO extends DataObject>
    and interface for Composite that support anonymisation. These should be called from the AnonymisingFactory.anonymise() method. They can ALSO be used to erase the data for specific users within a production database for data protection reasons.
